---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy · thelnk.is" description="How thelnk.is handles your data.">
  <article class="legal">
    <h1>Privacy</h1>
    <p class="lead">Last updated: June 2026</p>

    <p>
      thelnk.is is a link-in-bio service: you claim a username and publish a public page of links.
      This policy explains what we collect, why, and who we share it with.
    </p>

    <h2>What we collect</h2>
    <p>
      <strong>Account data</strong> — when you sign up, our authentication provider gives us an account
      identifier and the email address you sign in with. <strong>Profile data</strong> — the username you
      claim and anything you add to your page (display name, bio, links, and, in future, photos and
      products). <strong>Technical data</strong> — standard request information such as IP address and
      user agent, processed to deliver and secure the site.
    </p>

    <h2>Your page is public</h2>
    <p>
      Your profile at <code>thelnk.is/your-username</code> and everything you choose to show on it are
      <strong>public by design</strong> — that's the point of the product. Don't put anything on your page
      you wouldn't want publicly visible.
    </p>

    <h2>Authentication</h2>
    <p>
      Sign-in and account management are provided by <a href="https://clerk.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Clerk</a>.
      Clerk's privacy policy governs the authentication data they process on our behalf. We do not store
      your password.
    </p>

    <h2>Hosting and logs</h2>
    <p>
      The service runs on <a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Cloudflare</a>
      (Workers, D1, R2, and related products). Cloudflare may process IP addresses and technical data as
      part of delivering and securing the site.
    </p>

    <h2>Cookies</h2>
    <p>
      We use only the cookies required to keep you signed in and operate the service. We don't use
      third-party advertising cookies.
    </p>

    <h2>Payments</h2>
    <p>
      Paid features and selling are not yet available. If and when we add them, payment processing will be
      handled by a third-party processor (such as <a href="https://stripe.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Stripe</a>),
      we won't store full card numbers, and this policy will be updated before any charge is possible.
    </p>

    <h2>Your choices</h2>
    <p>
      You can edit or remove links and profile details at any time from your dashboard. To delete your
      account and associated profile data, contact us at the address below.
    </p>

    <h2>Children</h2>
    <p>thelnk.is is not directed to children under 13, and we don't knowingly collect their data.</p>

    <h2>Changes</h2>
    <p>
      We may update this policy as the product evolves. Material changes will be reflected by the “last
      updated” date above.
    </p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions about privacy? Email <a href="mailto:hello@thelnk.is">hello@thelnk.is</a>.</p>

    <p class="back"><a href="/">← Back home</a></p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .legal {
    max-width: 42rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4rem) 1.5rem 4rem;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--muted);
  }
  .legal h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 2.6rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--text);
    margin: 0 0 0.4rem;
  }
  .legal .lead {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    color: var(--muted-2);
    margin: 0 0 2rem;
  }
  .legal h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text);
    margin: 2.25rem 0 0.6rem;
  }
  .legal p { margin: 0 0 1rem; }
  .legal a { color: var(--accent); }
  .legal a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
  .legal strong { color: var(--text-dim); }
  .legal code {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.85em;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 0.1em 0.4em;
  }
  .legal .back { margin-top: 2.5rem; }
</style>
